sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_vegetarian_desserts
FROM desserts
WHERE is_vegetarian = 1;

external_knowledge:
Popular desserts refers to those with more than one review; 
Sorted by average ratings means that the dessert with the highest rating comes first, followed by the one with the second highest, and so on;
Sorted by review counts means that if two desserts have the same average rating, the dessert with more reviews will be ranked higher.

